Install Gems

  sudo gem install merb 0.9.5
  sudo gem install merb-auth
  sudo gem install merb_paginate
  sudo gem install merb_has_flash
  sudo gem install merb-mailer
  sudo gem install merb-slices
 
  Following instruction are for installing merb-auth for login functionality through GitHub.
  
  Grab the source in to the application and install the gem 

    git clone git://github.com/hassox/merb-auth.git 
    cd merb-auth 
    sudo rake install

  Copy missing files
    cp lib/constantz.rb.sample lib/constantz.rb

  Start Merb
    merb -p 4000
